e dub for unclear reasons.\n\n<gallery>\nSM052 Dub Edit Original.png|Scene from the original showing\nSM052 Dub Edit.png|Scene edited in the dub\n</gallery>\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Epilang|color=90BDDC|bordercolor=F1912B\n|zh_cmn={{tt|日輪祭壇！索爾迦雷歐降臨！！|The Altar of the Sunne! Solgaleo Descends!!}}\n|cs={{tt|Odhalení podstaty legendy!|Revealing the essence of a legend!}}\n|da={{tt|Legendariske afsløringer!|Legendary revelations!}}\n|fi={{tt|Legendan aineksia paljastamassa!|Revealing the stuff of legend!}}\n|nl={{tt|Legendarische onthullingen!|Legendary revelations!}}\n|fr_eu={{tt|La révélation d\'une légende !|The revelation of a legend!}}\n|de={{tt|Die Enthüllung einer Legende!|The revelation of a legend!}}\n|he={{tt|!גילוי אגדי|A Legendary Revelation!}}\n|it={{tt|La leggenda diventa realtà!|The legend becomes reality!}}\n|ko={{tt|일륜의 제단! 솔가레오 강림!!|The Altar of the Sunne! Solgaleo Descends!!}}\n|no={{tt|Legendariske avsløringer!|Legendary revelations!}}\n|pl={{tt|Odkrycie sedna legendy!|Revealing the stuff of legend!}}\n|pt_br={{tt|Revelando a lenda!|Revealing the legend!}}\n|pt_eu={{tt|A lenda em ação!|The legend on the action!}}\n|ru={{tt|Открытие легенды!|Revelation of a legend!}}\n|es_la={{tt|¡Revelación legendaria!|Legendary revelation!}}\n|es_eu={{tt|¡La revelación de una leyenda!|The revelation of a legend!}}\n|sv={{tt|En Legendarisk Upptäckt|A Legendary Discovery}}\n|th={{tt|แท่นบูชาสุริยัน! โซลกาเลโอจุติ!!|The Altar of the Sunne! Solgaleo Descends!!}}\n|tr={{tt|Efsanenin Özünü Ortaya Çıkarmak!|Uncovering the Stuff of Legend!}}\n}}\n{{-}}\n{{EpicodePrevNext|\nprevcode=SM051 |\nprevtitle=Family Determination! |\nnextcode=SM053 |\nnexttitle=Rescuing the Unwilling! |\nseries=Sun & Moon series |\ncolorscheme=Alola}}\n{{Project Anime notice}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:0991}}\n[[Category:Sun & Moon series episodes|052]]\n[[Category:Episodes written by Aya Matsui]]\n[[Category:Episodes storyboarded and directed by Maki Kodaira]]\n[[Category:Episodes storyboarded by Maki K